Comment: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.91,Sample KM [Down] ALLGM 14 if size 16,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wherever I go, the conclusion is:
Comment: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:40.99,Sample KM [Down] ALLGM 14 if size 16,,0,0,0,karaoke,I want to be with you
Comment: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.78,Sample KM [Down] ALLGM 14 if size 16,,0,0,0,karaoke,I'm sure your future self
